node.text:
Within this finca in Ibiza, a quiet and charming retreat to enjoy the peaceful island life, this wellness oasis provides a contemporary feel whilst retaining the rusticity of the building. 

The interplay between its Ibicencan aesthetic and some refined @antoniolupidesign pieces like the #Borghi washbasin with the Borghi_180 tub in Mostato #Cristalmood, the #Tramato carpet with our #Tralerighe wallpaper, the #Apollo showerheads, creates an harmonious eclectic environment that maximize the interactions between light and space, textures and colors, function and flows.

#antoniolupi #italiandesign #bathroomdesign #homestyling #wellnessdesign
